Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|3\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|1\u20132<ref name=\"Spurs v Benfica\"/>\n| 4\u20133\n|-\n| [[1962 European Cup Final|F]]\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Spain|1945}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20133<ref name=\"Real Madrid v Benfica\"/>\n|-\n| [[1962 Intercontinental Cup|1962]]\n| align=\"left\"|Intercontinental Cup\n| {{n/a}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Brazil|1960}} [[Santos FC|Santos]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|2\u20135\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|2\u20133\n| 0pts\u20134pts\n|-\n| rowspan=5|[[1962\u201363 European Cup|1962\u201363]]\n| rowspan=15 align=\"left\"|European Cup\n| {{Tooltip|PR|Preliminary round}}\n| colspan=4|Bye\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R1|Round 1}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Sweden}} [[IFK Norrk\u00f6ping]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|1\u20131\n| 6\u20132\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|QF|Quarter-finals}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Czechoslovakia}} [[Dukla Prague]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|2\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|0\u20130\n| 2\u20131\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|SF|Semi-finals}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Feyenoord]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|3\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|0\u20130\n| 3\u20131\n|-\n| [[1963 European Cup Final|F]]\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Italy}} [[A.C. Milan|Milan]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|1\u20132<ref name=\"Milan v Benfica\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[1963\u201364 European Cup|1963\u201364]]\n| {{Tooltip|PR|Preliminary round}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Northern Ireland}} [[Lisburn Distillery F.C.|Lisburn Distillery]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|3\u20133\n| 8\u20133\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R1|Round 1}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|West Germany}} [[Borussia Dortmund]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|2\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|0\u20135\n| 2\u20136\n|-\n| rowspan=5|[[1964\u201365 European Cup|1964\u201365]]\n| {{Tooltip|PR|Preliminary round}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Luxembourg}} [[FC Aris Bonnevoie|Aris Bonnevoie]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20131\n| 10\u20132\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R1|Round 1}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Switzerland}} [[FC La Chaux-de-Fonds|La Chaux-de-Fonds]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|1\u20131\n| 6\u20131\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|QF|Quarter-finals}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Spain|1945}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|5\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|1\u20133\n| 6\u20133\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|SF|Semi-finals}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Gy\u0151ri ETO FC|Gy\u0151ri Vasas ETO]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|4\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|1\u20130\n| 5\u20130\n|-\n| [[1965 European Cup Final|F]]\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Italy}} [[Inter Milan]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|0\u20131\n|-\n| rowspan=3|[[1965\u201366 European Cup|1965\u201366]]\n| {{Tooltip|PR|Preliminary round}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Luxembourg}} [[Stade Dudelange]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|10\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|8\u20130\n| 18\u20130\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R1|Round 1}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Bulgaria|1946}} [[PFC Levski Sofia|Levski Sofia]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|3\u20132\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|2\u20132\n| 5\u20134\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|QF|Quarter-finals}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|England}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|1\u20135\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|2\u20133\n| 3\u20138\n|-\n| rowspan=3|[[1966\u201367 Inter-Cities Fairs Cup|1966\u201367]]\n| rowspan=3 align=\"left\"|[[Inter-Cities Fairs Cup]]\n| {{Tooltip|R1|Round 1}}\n| colspan=4|Bye\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R2|Round 2}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Bulgaria|1946}} [[FC Spartak Plovdiv|Spartak Plovdiv]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|3\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"|1\u20131\n| 4\u20131\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|R3|Round 3}}\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|East Germany}} [[1. FC Lokomotive Leipzig|Lokomotive Leipzig]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"|2\u20131\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"|1\u20133\n| 3